{"id":8546,"date":"2023-12-04T14:18:44","date_gmt":"2023-12-04T07:18:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/?p=8546"},"modified":"2024-12-07T11:41:24","modified_gmt":"2024-12-07T04:41:24","slug":"thanh-toan-tt","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/thanh-toan-tt\/","title":{"rendered":"Thanh to\u00e1n TT l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c Telegraphic Transfer payment?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Thanh to\u00e1n TT l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/strong>? <strong>Telegraphic Transfer<\/strong> c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c thanh to\u00e1n n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u? Tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, k\u00e9o theo c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c thanh to\u00e1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n theo.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c thanh to\u00e1n. <strong>Thanh to\u00e1n TT<\/strong> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c giao d\u1ecbch ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eady h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <strong>ISO Logistics<\/strong> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 <strong>ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c thanh to\u00e1n TT l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/strong> qua n\u1ed9i dung sau nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8547 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/thanh-toan-tt.jpg\" alt=\"Thanh to\u00e1n TT l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/iso-logistics.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/t